{"tid":2169678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(恐怖慎入) 有人拍左條恐怖片反諷政治正確，點知真實仲恐怖","createTime":"2020-08-22T16:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T17:45:25.000Z","uid":84147,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63a5529b42a4d0de48acd5bf34259151b060bd64","tid":2169678,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lt7AD6f8y2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flt7AD6f8y2o&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6YBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=477fcfef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lt7AD6f8y2o</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n段片本身已經好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗清楚後寒左寒，個亞裔男所代表的形象明明係講緊黑人 (下層，唔聰明，懶，讀書廢)<br />\n同美國的亞裔根本係好大分別 (聰明，努力，讀書勁)<br />\n但因為如果由黑人演，個導演一定會比人批鬥到收皮<br />\n由白人演又表達唔到個concept，無理由成班人都係白人<span class=\"red\"><br />\n<strong>所以個角色變左由亞裔演，亦只能由亞裔演</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n因為真實的亞裔同片入邊的亞裔剛剛相反 (片入邊亞裔最高分拎哂福利)<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>黑人白人唔可以歧視，而真實的亞裔就算係片到比人歧視係弱智都無問題<br />\n</strong></span>而且亞裔係唔會有特權，所以導演搵左個亞裔演黑人角色"},{"pid":"8867df0ac240bfdd748cca76324ebf3324623e89","tid":2169678,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3918ce570977f8a666c3ebf3c7c0e51fb44ab7f0","tid":2169678,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h